<lb n="6"/>καὶ εἶδεν ὁ <expan>θ<ex>εὸ</ex>ς</expan> τὸ φ<supplied reason="lost">ῶ</supplied>ς <choice><reg>ὅτι</reg><orig>ὅτει</orig></choice> καλόν. καὶ δι<supplied reason="lost">ε</supplied>χώ
