<lb n="12" break="no"/>θέν. <unclear>καὶ</unclear> <supplied reason="lost">ε</supplied>ἶπεν <expan>θ<ex>εό</ex>ς</expan>· <supplied reason="lost">γ</supplied>ε<supplied reason="lost">ν</supplied>ηθήτω φῶ<supplied reason="lost">ς. καὶ</supplied>
