<lb n="16"/>καὶ <gap reason="lost" quantity="4" unit="character"/> <supplied reason="lost">π</supplied><unclear>ρ</unclear>ωί, <unclear>ἡ</unclear><supplied reason="lost">μ</supplied>έρα <num value="1">πρώτη</num><g rend="extension" type="filler"/>
</ab> </div>
</div></div>
         <div type="commentary" subtype="linebyline">
            <list>
               <item corresp="#div3-div3-lb8" xml:space="preserve"><ref>8</ref> <p>After σκότους the scribe omits καὶ ἐκάλεσεν ... νύκτα. So too in l. 15.</p></item>
               <item corresp="#div3-div3-lb14" xml:space="preserve"><ref>14</ref> <p>The traces before διεχ[ do not suit καὶ.</p></item>
               <item corresp="#div3-div3-lb15" xml:space="preserve"><ref>15</ref> <p>As in l. 8, after σκότους the scribe omits καὶ ἐκάλεσεν ... νύκτα.</p></item>
            </list>
